com.ibm.ecm.api.coresdk.collection

Interface IBMECMItemPermissions

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Iterable<IBMECMAccessControlEntry>

    public interface IBMECMItemPermissions
extends Iterable<IBMECMAccessControlEntry>
    Represents a collection for IBMECMAccessControlEntry instances.
